OL,4,Cseized
OL,6,FTwo illegally adapted e-scooters which
OL,7,Fposed an "incredibly serious risk"
OL,8,Fhave been seized by police.
OL,10,FOne of the e-scooters had been adapted
OL,11,Fwith a motor and was capable of
OL,12,Freaching speeds of up to 90 miles per
OL,13,Fhour.
OL,15,FLancashire Police's Hyndburn
OL,16,FNeighbourhood Policing Team, and the
OL,17,FRoads Policing Unit, seized the e-
OL,18,Fscooters in Rishton on Thursday 4
OL,19,FSeptember following concerns raised by
OL,20,Fresidents in the local area.
