OL,6,FNeighbourhood Policing Inspector for
OL,7,Fthe area, Mo Lorgat, said: "The
OL,8,Fcommunity tell us on social media and
OL,9,Fvia our Lancashire Talking survey that
OL,10,Fe-bikes and e-scooters are a priority
OL,11,Fconcern.
OL,13,F"The scooter we have seized could
OL,14,Freach speeds of 90mph, and this poses
OL,15,Fan incredibly serious risk to the
OL,16,Frider, other road users and
OL,17,Fpedestrians going about their daily
OL,18,Fbusiness.
