OL,6,F"Through Op Centurion, we will
OL,7,Fcontinue to address the issue of these
OL,8,Fillegally adapted bikes and scooters,
OL,9,Fand I would urge anyone who spots them
OL,10,Fto report it to us."
OL,12,FOperation Centurion is a county-wide
OL,13,Finitiative targeting anti-social
OL,14,Fbehaviour, including the illegal use
OL,15,Fof e-bikes, e-scooters, and general
OL,16,Fmotorbike nuisance.
